# Hopsbook: A Guide to Getting Started with Homelabbing  

Welcome to **Hopsbook**! Our goal is to create an open-source informational booklet to help others understand and get into the field of homelabbing. Whether you're new to homelabs or looking to expand your knowledge, this book will prepare you before and during your homelab adventure.

## ðŸ“– What is Hopsbook?

Hopsbook is a community-driven project that aims to provide clear, beginner-friendly, and practical guidance on homelabbing. We believe in learning by doing, and our book will serve as a starting point for those interested in setting up their own home labs.

